    "We discuss related work in Section 4 and conclude in Section 5.",
    "In Section 2.1, we give a mathematical formulation for our motivating application, the Suggested Response (SR) problem.",
    "Then, in Section 2.2, we provide an illustrative example to provide additional intuition on the key trade-offs that exist in the SR setting.",
    "A conversation between a business and a customer is a sequence of messages c 1, m 1,.",
    ", c n, m n where a customer sends message c i and a business responds with message m i."
